msgid "Idha, bhante, ekacco anabhijjhālu hoti, anabhijjhāsahagatāya saññāya viharati; "
msgstr "It’s when someone is content, and lives with their perception full of contentment. "

msgctxt "mn114:9.15"
msgid "abyāpādavā hoti, abyāpādasahagatāya saññāya viharati; "
msgstr "They have good will, and live with their perception full of good will. "

msgctxt "mn114:9.16"
msgid "avihesavā hoti, avihesāsahagatāya saññāya viharati—"
