msgctxt "mn114:48.2"
msgid "sevitabbampi, asevitabbampī’ti—"
msgstr "that which you should cultivate, and that which you should not cultivate.’ "

msgctxt "mn114:48.3"
msgid "iti kho panetaṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā. "
msgstr "That’s what the Buddha said, "

msgctxt "mn114:48.4"
msgid "Kiñcetaṃ paṭicca vuttaṃ? "
msgstr "but why did he say it? "

msgctxt "mn114:48.5"
msgid "Yathārūpaṃ, bhante, puggalaṃ sevato akusalā dhammā abhivaḍḍhanti, kusalā dhammā parihāyanti evarūpo puggalo na sevitabbo; "
msgstr "You should not cultivate the kind of person who causes unskillful qualities to grow while skillful qualities decline. "

msgctxt "mn114:48.6"
msgid "yathārūpañca kho, bhante, puggalaṃ sevato akusalā dhammā parihāyanti, kusalā dhammā abhivaḍḍhanti evarūpo puggalo sevitabbo. "
msgstr "And you should cultivate the kind of person who causes unskillful qualities to decline while skillful qualities grow. "

msgctxt "mn114:48.7"
msgid "‘Puggalaṃpāhaṃ, sāriputta, duvidhena vadāmi—"
msgstr "‘I say that there are two kinds of person: "

msgctxt "mn114:48.8"
msgid "sevitabbampi, asevitabbampī’ti—"
msgstr "those who you should cultivate, and those who you should not cultivate.’ "

msgctxt "mn114:48.9"
msgid "iti yaṃ taṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā idametaṃ paṭicca vuttanti. "
msgstr "That’s what the Buddha said, and this is why he said it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya49
msgctxt "mn114:49.1"
msgid "Imassa kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa, vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa evaṃ vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāmī”ti. "
msgstr "Sir, that’s how I understand the detailed meaning of the Buddha’s brief statement.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya50, pts-vp-pli3.60, sc43
msgctxt "mn114:50.1"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, sāriputta. "
msgstr "“Good, good, Sāriputta! "

msgctxt "mn114:50.2"
msgid "Sādhu kho tvaṃ, sāriputta, imassa mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa, vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa evaṃ vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāsi. "
msgstr "It’s good that you understand the detailed meaning of my brief statement in this way.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya51-58
msgctxt "mn114:51-58.1"
msgid "‘Cīvaraṃpāhaṃ, sāriputta, duvidhena vadāmi—"
